data.description: 4 BEDROOM GEM AND ONLY 5 YEARS OLD !  Desired area north of I-12 and not far from Southeastern LA University. 4 bedrooms / 2 bath, a spacious 2 car garage, back patio with view to beautiful trees. Kitchen has a large island with beautiful granite along with the countertops and multiple cabinets. 4th bedroom or bonus room upstairs is extra large for a play area, office area or entertaining. Wired and plumbed for a home generator install! Some flooring and minor repairs will need to be addressed from previous pets in home and price is in accordance with the current condition.  Seller is willing to negotiate a higher price of $295 with the grant of a $20K repair allowance. Funds can be escrowed with title company/attorney office so Buyer can have contractor fix issues at hand and install new flooring and paint. Don't miss out on this Win-Win Situation !
